                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6999" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0161</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7587 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">银河期货青岛：勇担投资者教育责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Qingdao Branch of Galaxy Futures: Undertake the Responsibility of Investor Education</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">安康，王洪生（通讯作者），朱萌萌，王磊，刘娟，蒲小彤</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">山东农业大学*</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">银河期货有限公司青岛营业部</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">决策型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">银河期货青岛；投资者教育；金融知识进校园；社会责任</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Qingdao Business Department of Galaxy Futures; Investor education; Financial knowledge into the campus; The social responsibility</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020年，突发的新冠疫情对各行各业产生巨大影响，然而国内资本市场热度不减，市场的参与度及成交数量不减反增。与此同时我国金融市场建设不足、金融人才欠缺、投资者教育缺口大等问题可见一斑；随着新法规、新品种、新规则的不断推出，投资者教育和保护工作任重道远。本案例以银河期货青岛营业部领导人庞大为的第一人称，讲述了在国家出台多项政策法规鼓励金融机构开展投资者教育活动的背景下，银河期货青岛营业部先试先行，扛起金融投教责任的大旗。在保证专业期货人才队伍能力的前提下，开创多彩创新型投教产品，多元化宣传推广金融期货知识。同时借助“郑商所杯”的契机大力推进“金融知识进校园”活动，在做好风险教育、提高投资者金融素养的同时，构建专业人才链培养与校企联动的并行机制，为其他金融机构开展投资者教育和承担社会责任提供有效借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2020, the outbreak of COVID-19 has had a huge impact on all industries; However, the domestic capital market heat is not reduced, the market participation and the number of transactions is not reduced but increased. At the same time, China&#39;s financial market construction is insufficient, the lack of financial personnel, investor education gap and other problems can be seen. With the introduction of new regulations, new varieties and new rules, investor education and protection work is a long way to go. This case, based on the first person of Pang Da Wei, the leader of Qingdao business Department of Galaxy Futures, tells Galaxy Futures Qingdao Business Department to take the lead of financial investment and education under the premise that the state has issued a number of policies and regulations to encourage financial institutions to carry out investor education activities. How to create colorful and innovative investment teaching products and promote financial futures knowledge in a diversified way under the premise of ensuring the ability of professional futures talents. At the same time, with the opportunity of &quot;Zheng Business Suo Cup&quot;, vigorously promote the activity of &quot;Financial knowledge into campus&quot;, and build a parallel mechanism of professional talent chain training and school-enterprise linkage while doing a good job in risk education and improving investors&#39; financial literacy. It provides reference for other financial institutions to carry out investor education and undertake social responsibility.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业社会责任定义及金字塔模型；利益相关者理论；战略性社会责任概念，CSR与SCSR对比；发展战略与战略变革</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
